To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private RelativeDailyVolume _rdv;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_rdv = RDV(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_rdv.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "relativedailyvolume", _rdv.Current.Value);
}
